Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.76,0:00:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the very first...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.12,0:00:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...summer evening spooky story contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,~ Summer Evening Spooky Story Contest ~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.86,0:00:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even summer dude...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just play along!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all here to tell each other the scariest story we know!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! You're first, lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two wanna die again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A scary story, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once, when I was in Afghanistan, we were surrounded by the enemy, and our supplies got cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was really scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sis. How's that scary...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.84,0:01:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing scarier than having your supplies cut off when you're surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.59,0:01:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us one of your scary stories then!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.93,0:01:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One time I broke into this place, and it turned out to be a cop's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.06,0:01:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They get really pissed when one of their own gets killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.94,0:01:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made next to nothing and ended up on the run for months!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just the story of one of your blunders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a better one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.72,0:01:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Then I'll try...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard this from Maki-chan, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.07,0:01:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once when her friend stepped into the bathtub...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She slipped and jammed her toes really hard into the tiles...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looked at her foot, and the nail of her big toe was flapping up and down like a toilet lid...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:02:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a scary story. That's a painful story!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sniff, sniff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, yo. How about you tell us one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I heard this from somebody else, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This lady had a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she was being stalked and getting weird calls all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then one day she got a message on her phone saying, "three left."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She thought it was just another prank, as usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But one day she noticed her cat walking funny so she looked at its legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.31,0:03:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It had...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...one leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...chopped off...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd-a killed the bastard if I found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...act creeped out like a girl for once, will you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing fazes her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Rock! Then you tell us one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not such a good story, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.85,0:03:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This happened to an acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said ever since he heard a scary story about a little girl in a red skirt from a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...strange things started happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody paid attention at first...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...his friend called him late at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "a little girl in a red skirt's outside my window right now," and just hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So my friend went by his place later and found him dead, hanging from a beam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, I thought you could do better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask me, I'd say it's scary, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... There's more to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who's heard this story...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has seen a girl in a red skirt at their house within three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So watch out guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey? Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a story!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys were the ones who wanted to hear it! C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This week's scaredy-cat award
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.64,0:05:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All done!
